Class OpenC2BaseSection

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.oasis.openc2.lycan.utilities.OpenC2BaseSection

    OpenC2BaseTypeSection, OpenC2Modifier

    public class OpenC2BaseSection
extends java.lang.Object
    OC2BaseSection is the minimum set of variables and methods that are common to the target, actuator and modifier sections of an OpenC2 message.
